    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with a strong paint finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, providing a smooth ride and responsive handling with a complete service history available for review. It\u2019s a reliable, attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
