    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this well-maintained vehicle, representing a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has been kept to rigorous standards, ensuring mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic presence. It serves as an ideal selection for the professional seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience. Thoroughly inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, this vehicle offers a compelling opportunity for the discerning purchaser.",
