    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a great car. It's in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! It's the perfect daily driver for someone who wants something reliable that still looks sharp on the road. I've truly enjoyed owning this car and have taken good care of it, so I'd love to see it go to a happy new home. Feel free to message me if you have any questions\u2014I'm super easy to talk to and happy to help!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The high-strung induction system is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator overhauls, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), the suspension geometry remains true, offering a communicative chassis balance. While the exterior shows honest wear from enthusiast ownership, the powertrain remains a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Interior well-kept.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_4",
